name: Voxel Dreams: K-Food Series #03: The Chef's Makgolli Bio (막걸리 무농약)
description: The Chef transforms the traditional Makgeolli - a drink of humble people, composed of the third fermentation of low-alcohol rice bagasse - into an elite drink, fermented from organic rice grains from the region of Santa Catarina, Brazil, coming from the family farming plantations. The Chef Makgeolli is 100% ecofriendly, and its purity gives it a taste never before seen on the streets of Seoul. Created by The Chef and branded by The Philosopher.
